{"tid":1914081,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"根本係香港，做窮人好過做夾心中產","createTime":"2020-03-07T09:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T16:22:34.000Z","uid":149978,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"807bc673894adf7319d7792a40cbce61945fdc1c","tid":1914081,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:22:54.000Z","msg":"睇下些公屋，質素好過好多私人樓。<br />\n<br />\n在私人市場要租到公屋質素，真係要兩萬一個月。<br />\n<br />\n咩野水泉澳邨、安達邨，呢些質素質素，對公屋仔黎講，已經係十大最伏/最差公屋。<br />\n<br />\n早前班公屋仔話水泉澳和安達已經係最差公屋之一，咁私樓大多數都可以仆街收皮。<br />\n<br />\n除非係住緊高尚住宅/新私樓/700呎以上，否則都比唔上公屋仔。"},{"pid":"ec7d03175187de164664f66de3afc53b9f1328b5","tid":1914081,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"網民選最差公屋 新屋邨安達、水泉澳上榜 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/162165/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E9%81%B8%E6%9C%80%E5%B7%AE%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B-%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%8B%E9%82%A8%E5%AE%89%E9%81%94-%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%89%E6%BE%B3%E4%B8%8A%E6%A6%9C-%E5%AD%A4%E5%B3%B6%E5%86%87%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C%2F162165%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B1%258B%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2581%2594-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B3%2589%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25A6%259C-%25E5%25AD%25A4%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E5%2586%2587%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25BD&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=96422b1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/162165/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E9%81%B8%E6%9C%80%E5%B7%AE%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B-%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%8B%E9%82%A8%E5%AE%89%E9%81%94-%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%89%E6%BE%B3%E4%B8%8A%E6%A6%9C-%E5%AD%A4%E5%B3%B6%E5%86%87%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD</a><br />\n<br />\n班公屋你真係串到威到，連水泉澳和安達都睇唔上眼。"},{"pid":"d3f9f953626614ff555bb743bcd660b6d5ff777